00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:07,356
 ♫ Where to go ♫ 

259
00:17:07,356 --> 00:17:09,324
 ♫ How to escape ♫ 

260
00:17:09,324 --> 00:17:12,564
 He's quite handsome.
But he doesn't have a proper job. 

261
00:17:12,564 --> 00:17:15,244
 Financial stability matters most. I must warn you. 

262
00:17:15,244 --> 00:17:17,244
 Dr. Gao is better than him. Right, sis? 

263
00:17:17,244 --> 00:17:20,944
 Yeah, I find him too withdrawn 

264
00:17:20,944 --> 00:17:22,620
 and complicated. 

265
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:24,324
 Look how innocent Meng is. 

266
00:17:24,324 --> 00:17:27,144
 She will be exhausted. 

267
00:17:27,144 --> 00:17:31,872
 I'm right here. I'll get mad
if you keep badmouthing Li Jin Yu. 

268
00:17:31,872 --> 00:17:35,256
 ♫ My words stuck in my throat ♫ 

269
00:17:35,256 --> 00:17:41,336
 ♫ Maybe this'll end the sorrow ♫ 

270
00:17:41,336 --> 00:17:45,597
 ♫ Pretending to be determined ♫ 

271
00:17:45,597 --> 00:17:51,444
 ♫ I'm still trapped at the starting point ♫ 

272
00:17:53,346 --> 00:17:56,381
 ♫ The most perfect lie ♫ 

273
00:17:56,381 --> 00:17:59,437
 ♫ I even deceive myself ♫ 

274
00:17:59,437 --> 00:18:06,104
 ♫ If love means letting go Let's sever all connections ♫ 

275
00:18:06,104 --> 00:18:08,648
 ♫ But why ♫ 

276
