 ♫ The moment tears fall ♫ 

277
00:18:11,968 --> 00:18:16,121
 ♫ I don't want you to leave ♫ 

278
00:18:56,724 --> 00:19:00,664
Come here, son. Happy New Year. Wait.

279
00:19:00,664 --> 00:19:05,444
Mom wishes you health, safety, and growing tall.

280
00:19:05,444 --> 00:19:08,964
- Thanks, Mom. I wish you'd make more money.
- Alright.

281
00:19:08,964 --> 00:19:11,244
- And nag me less. 
 - Can't do that.

282
00:19:11,244 --> 00:19:13,504
You'd be unrestrained.

283
00:19:13,504 --> 00:19:15,804
Have some meat.

284
00:19:15,804 --> 00:19:18,304
Put your red envelope away.

285
00:19:19,944 --> 00:19:22,324
Who is it on Chinese New Year's Eve? Let me see.

286
00:19:22,324 --> 00:19:24,160
Coming.

287
00:19:24,980 --> 00:19:26,940
Who is it?

288
00:19:30,084 --> 00:19:31,444
Kai.

289
00:19:31,444 --> 00:19:33,484
Happy New Year, Ya En.

290
00:19:33,484 --> 00:19:37,784
Happy New Year.
Why aren't you having dinner at home?

291
00:19:37,784 --> 00:19:41,224
I was delivering New Year goods to clients
and brought you a share.

292
00:19:41,224 --> 00:19:43,404
- Thank you so much. 
 - My pleasure.

293
00:19:43,404 --> 00:19:46,164
Here's a red envelope for Jia Yu.

294
00:19:46,164 --> 00:19:49,664
- I can't accept this. 
 - Take it for the kid. Come on.

295
00:19:49,664 --> 00:19:51,724
Then I'll thank you on Jia Yu's behalf.

296
00:19:51,724 --> 00:19:53,584
Just a small gesture.

297
00:19:53,584 --> 00:19:57,084
I didn't know what Jia Yu likes, so I picked this.

298
00:19:57,084 --> 00:19:59,404
You're too kind, Kai.

299
00:19:59,404 --> 00:20:02,824
- It's the New Year. 
 - Give it to him yourself.

300
00:20:02,824 --> 00:20:05,124
- Alright. 
 - Let's go.

301
00:20:07,024 --> 00:20:10,884
Jia Yu. Look who's here.

302
00:20:10,884 --> 00:20:14,284
No need to change shoes. Come on in.

303
00:20:19,264 --> 00:20:21,844
Happy New Year, kiddo.

304
00:20:21,844 --> 00:20:25,844
Mom, do you owe him money?
Is this uncle here to collect debts?

305
00:20:25,844 --> 00:20:31,524
Mind your words. Greet him.
He prepared a red envelope for you.

306
00:20:31,524 --> 00:20:33,904
Happy New Year, Uncle.

307
00:20:33,904 --> 00:20:36,244
Happy New Year to you, too.

308
00:20:37,204 --> 00:20:42,984
This... This is a gift I picked for you.
See if you like it.

309
00:20:49,024 --> 00:20:53,736
Thank you, Uncle. This really matches your style.

310
00:20:55,328 --> 00:20:56,964
I like it very much.

311
00:20:56,964 --> 00:21:00,684
Glad you like it.
Tell me if you want any other toys.

312
00:21:00,684 --> 00:21:03,144
I'll get you toys until you're 18.

313
00:21:03,144 --> 00:21:07,244
No need. Money's hard to earn.
Don't waste your money on me.

314
00:21:07,244 --> 00:21:08,804
Mom, I'll put this away.

315
00:21:08,804 --> 00:21:10,644
Go ahead.

316
00:21:10,644 --> 00:21:12,744
So clueless.

317
00:21:14,164 --> 00:21:16,984
High EQ, huh? He takes after me.

318
00:21:16,984 --> 00:21:18,724
Come on, eat something.

319
00:21:18,724 --> 00:21:20,404
I should head back now.

320
00:21:20,404 --> 00:21:23,764
Come on. Have a drink for the New Year.

321
00:21:23,764 --> 00:21:26,464
Also, try my cooking.

322
00:21:26,464 --> 00:21:29,564
It's a clean glass. Want some beer?

323
00:21:32,324 --> 00:21:36,544
You've changed a lot over the years.

324
00:21:36,544 --> 00:21:39,444
You've changed way more.

325
00:21:39,444 --> 00:21:41,904
My son thought you were a debt collector.

326
00:21:41,904 --> 00:21:45,944
Do you know what kids think of you?

327
00:21:45,944 --> 00:21:50,484
I'm removing this scar after the festival.

328
00:21:50,484 --> 00:21:52,524
You're acting weird.

329
00:21:54,224 --> 00:21:58,464
You came to fix your suit. Now, scar removal?

330
00:21:58,464 --> 00:22:00,684
You're into someone, huh?

331
00:22:02,344 --> 00:22:04,064
No.

332
00:22:04,064 --> 00:22:05,844
Really?

333
00:22:05,844 --> 00:22:07,244
Really.

334
00:22:07,244 --> 00:22:09,804
You can tell me. I can give you advice.

335
00:22:09,804 --> 00:22:11,724
It's a small town. Who would I like?

336
00:22:11,724 --> 00:22:13,554
There are so many pretty girls here.

337
00:22:13,554 --> 00:22:15,444
I bet someone meets your standards.

338
00:22:15,444 --> 00:22:18,984
I'm not into anyone. I-I should go now.

339
00:22:18,984 --> 00:22:21,264
My dad's waiting to cook dumplings.

340
00:22:21,264 --> 00:22:24,944
Right, bring Ye Meng
to my shop after the Spring Festival.

341
00:22:24,944 --> 00:22:29,264
Eat something first. You haven't had dinner.

342
00:22:29,264 --> 00:22:31,544
This book is for you.

343
00:22:32,504 --> 00:22:34,590
 

344
00:22:36,404 --> 00:22:39,724
Reciprocity. Knowledge strengthens the mind.

345
00:22:40,924 --> 00:22:42,564
Isn't it strange?

346
00:22:42,564 --> 00:22:47,244
With my low education level, I have such a studious son.

347
00:22:47,244 --> 00:22:50,924
Mom, you married Dad because you lacked education.

348
00:22:50,924 --> 00:22:54,664
So I learned from your mistake.

349
00:22:54,664 --> 00:22:57,084
True. Can't argue with that.

350
00:22:57,084 --> 00:23:01,964
Kids speak frankly.
I'll read the book and learn from it.

351
00:23:01,964 --> 00:23:03,944
I'm off. Call me if needed.

352
00:23:03,944 --> 00:23:06,404
Let me walk you out. Be right back.

353
00:23:06,404 --> 00:23:09,344
- Bye, Uncle. 
 - Goodbye.

354
00:23:09,344 --> 00:23:11,844
- I really like him. 
 - He likes you, too.

355
00:23:11,844 --> 00:23:14,024
- Really?
- Yeah.

356
00:23:14,024 --> 00:23:16,424
I'm off then. Go inside. It's cold.

357
00:23:16,424 --> 00:23:18,404
Okay. Take care.

358
00:23:18,404 --> 00:23:20,984
What are you doing here on New Year's Eve?

359
00:23:20,984 --> 00:23:23,744
I should ask you. Why are you here?

360
00:23:23,744 --> 00:23:26,204
To see my son.

361
00:23:26,204 --> 00:23:29,824
We're still married. Do you have to be so mean?

362
00:23:31,504 --> 00:23:34,004
My regards to your parents.

363
00:23:34,004 --> 00:23:35,624
Fine. I'm leaving.

364
00:23:35,624 --> 00:23:38,420
- Okay. Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

365
00:23:38,944 --> 00:23:43,324
A family is supposed to have dinner on New Year's Eve.

366
00:23:43,324 --> 00:23:46,524
- What are we having?
- Food is ready.

367
00:23:48,084 --> 00:23:49,984
Have you cooked dumplings?

368
00:24:22,444 --> 00:24:26,444
 I find him too withdrawn and complicated. 

369
00:24:26,444 --> 00:24:29,084
 Look how innocent Meng is. 

370
00:24:36,692 --> 00:24:39,300
 

371
00:24:49,064 --> 00:24:51,064
- Hello? 
 -  Hello? 

372
00:24:51,064 --> 00:24:52,984
Home yet?

373
00:24:54,644 --> 00:24:56,344
Just arrived.

374
00:24:58,264 --> 00:25:00,064
Feeding the fish?

375
00:25:04,824 --> 00:25:10,404
Remember the black goldfish you said resembled me?

376
00:25:10,404 --> 00:25:13,644
Of course. Why?

377
00:25:13,644 --> 00:25:18,804
You'll find a partner just like your goldfish did?

378
00:25:19,584 --> 00:25:25,604
That fish wasn't black in the first place.
It wasn't cool at all.

379
00:25:29,844 --> 00:25:34,544
It was red, just like the normal goldfish.

380
00:25:34,544 --> 00:25:39,544
It turned black because it
developed black spot disease.

381
00:25:40,604 --> 00:25:42,604
Black spot disease?

382
00:25:45,604 --> 00:25:47,740
It's a contagious disease.

383
00:25:49,290 --> 00:25:55,420
One of the goldfish has been infected.

384
00:25:59,344 --> 00:26:01,244
What are you trying to say?

385
00:26:02,604 --> 00:26:04,304
Ye Meng.

386
00:26:10,524 --> 00:26:14,044
If you encounter a sick goldfish,

387
00:26:15,924 --> 00:26:20,524
the best thing to do is to stay away from it.

388
00:26:20,524 --> 00:26:23,144
Don't try to get closer.

389
00:26:24,924 --> 00:26:29,984
Because it'll only drag you into the darkness.

390
00:26:38,404 --> 00:26:42,604
Your partner shouldn't be someone like me,

391
00:26:43,684 --> 00:26:46,420
who can't watch fireworks with you

392
00:26:47,410 --> 00:26:50,960
or celebrate New Year's Eve with your family.

393
00:26:52,348 --> 00:26:57,992
 ♫ Oh you, whispering softly ♫ 

394
00:26:59,296 --> 00:27:05,248
 ♫ Those restless anxieties ♫ 

395
00:27:06,588 --> 00:27:09,948
 ♫ Perhaps you're just like me ♫ 

396
00:27:09,948 --> 00:27:13,436
 ♫ Afraid of the pain of losing something ♫ 

397
00:27:13,436 --> 00:27:19,960
 ♫ That's why you chose to be silent ♫ 

398
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:27,648
 ♫ Hold me. Let time stand still ♫ 

399
00:27:27,648 --> 00:27:34,700
 ♫ How to let go of fading memories ♫ 

400
00:27:34,700 --> 00:27:41,570
 ♫ Memories flash by, gathering into rivers ♫ 

401
00:27:41,570 --> 00:27:48,764
 ♫ Buried deep in my heart ♫ 

402
00:27:48,764 --> 00:27:54,288
 ♫ My love is too obsessive ♫ 

403
00:27:54,288 --> 00:27:57,497
 ♫ My words are too harsh ♫ 

404
00:27:57,497 --> 00:28:01,372
 ♫ How to make you ♫ 

405
00:28:01,372 --> 00:28:04,636
 ♫ Understand me ♫ 

406
00:28:04,636 --> 00:28:07,906
 ♫ The promises I made ♫ 

407
00:28:07,906 --> 00:28:10,059
 ♫ I still remember ♫ 

408
00:28:10,059 --> 00:28:15,250
 ♫ Please don't forget ♫ 

409
00:28:32,624 --> 00:28:34,224
Ye Meng.

410
00:28:36,444 --> 00:28:38,780
Li Jin Yu,

411
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:43,380
I really don't understand.
Why can't you be brave for once?

412
00:28:43,384 --> 00:28:47,724
I've taken 99 steps toward you.
I just need you to take one step.

413
00:28:47,724 --> 00:28:51,144
I'm going to ditch you. Do you believe me?

414
00:28:59,292 --> 00:29:04,818
 ♫ My love is too obsessive ♫ 

415
00:29:04,818 --> 00:29:08,006
 ♫ My words are too harsh ♫ 

416
00:29:08,006 --> 00:29:11,936
 ♫ How to make you ♫ 

417
00:29:11,936 --> 00:29:15,292
 ♫ Understand me ♫ 

418
00:29:15,292 --> 00:29:18,364
 ♫ The promises I made ♫ 

419
00:29:18,364 --> 00:29:20,453
 ♫ I still remember ♫ 

420
00:29:20,453 --> 00:29:27,740
 ♫ Please don't forget me ♫ 

421
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:32,936
 ♫ I shouldn't have been so obsessed ♫ 

422
00:29:32,936 --> 00:29:34,944
 ♫ A moth drawn to flame ♫ 

423
00:29:34,944 --> 00:29:41,680
 ♫ Wounded all over, yet my love burns bright ♫ 

424
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:48,692
 ♫ If I'm just summer night's fleeting spark ♫ 

425
00:29:48,692 --> 00:29:58,685
 ♫ Remember I blazed for you ♫ 

426
00:30:11,784 --> 00:30:15,004
The Spring Festival is finally over.
I'm so exhausted.

427
00:30:15,004 --> 00:30:18,864
Chen Jian keeps coming over
every other day. So annoying.

428
00:30:18,864 --> 00:30:21,904
- What does he want now? 
 - Who knows?

429
00:30:21,904 --> 00:30:27,084
He's probably changed his mind because my shop's doing well lately.

430
00:30:27,084 --> 00:30:29,044
Unbelievable.

431
00:30:30,004 --> 00:30:34,964
You came here right after the Spring Festival
instead of visiting your neighbor boy?

432
00:30:34,964 --> 00:30:37,004
I won't see him again.

433
00:30:38,644 --> 00:30:40,644
What happened?

434
00:30:41,484 --> 00:30:44,164
I'm tired of pursuing him.

435
00:30:44,164 --> 00:30:48,124
But you said things were going well just days ago.

436
00:30:50,244 --> 00:30:52,284
He rejected me.

437
00:31:17,324 --> 00:31:19,224
Li Jin Yu.

438
00:31:45,224 --> 00:31:48,324
You brat. Where is that camera?

439
00:31:54,344 --> 00:31:56,690
He rejected you?

440
00:31:57,430 --> 00:32:00,380
A gorgeous, wealthy woman is pursuing him.

441
00:32:00,384 --> 00:32:05,244
He should be grateful,
yet he rejected you? This is ridiculous.

442
00:32:06,604 --> 00:32:11,764
He said he was afraid of dragging me down
as I try to save him.

443
00:32:11,764 --> 00:32:13,564
He told me to find a better man.

444
00:32:13,564 --> 00:32:16,614
He's even more demanding than a goldfish.

445
00:32:16,614 --> 00:32:19,084
You can't be too cold or too warm towards him.

446
00:32:19,084 --> 00:32:21,004
Care for him, and he calls you a do-gooder.

447
00:32:21,004 --> 00:32:24,364
Ignore him, and he'll just wither away quietly.

448
00:32:24,364 --> 00:32:26,264
So exhausting.

449
00:32:27,404 --> 00:32:30,804
So what's your plan? Are you giving up?

450
00:32:30,804 --> 00:32:34,864
What else can I do? He made himself clear.

451
00:32:35,724 --> 00:32:41,424
I totally support you.
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

452
00:32:47,284 --> 00:32:49,484
Speaking of the devil.

453
00:32:55,884 --> 00:33:00,204
He's not here for me. Has he been coming often?

454
00:33:00,204 --> 00:33:04,104
I suspect he knows you fell out with Li Jin Yu

455
00:33:04,104 --> 00:33:07,988
and wanted to approach you through me.

456
00:33:07,988 --> 00:33:10,684
Maybe he wants to pursue you.

457
00:33:10,684 --> 00:33:13,584
- You're crazy. 
 - I'm serious.

458
00:33:18,484 --> 00:33:22,664
Kai, come in.

459
00:33:22,664 --> 00:33:25,084
What a small world. Just a second.

460
00:33:25,084 --> 00:33:27,964
- That's it. Talk later. 
 - So awkward.

461
00:33:29,244 --> 00:33:31,244
What a coincidence.

462
00:33:31,984 --> 00:33:36,444
I happen to have
an unsweetened hot bubble tea in the car.

463
00:33:36,444 --> 00:33:38,144
Thanks.

464
00:33:43,424 --> 00:33:45,984
- Here's another cup. 
 - Thank you.

465
00:33:45,984 --> 00:33:49,724
What a small world. Why are you both here?

466
00:33:50,464 --> 00:33:53,624
Got something to say or not?

467
00:33:53,624 --> 00:33:57,104
I guess it's obvious.

468
00:33:58,424 --> 00:34:02,824
By the way, I reinstated Li Jin Yu at work.

469
00:34:04,204 --> 00:34:05,484
Why are you telling me this?

470
00:34:05,484 --> 00:34:09,484
Didn't you tell me to be magnanimous?

471
00:34:09,484 --> 00:34:11,964
Things have changed.

472
00:34:11,964 --> 00:34:13,504
Did I say that?

473
00:34:13,504 --> 00:34:17,760
Besides, I don't have anything
against Li Jin Yu.

474
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,640
We're buddies.

475
00:34:20,264 --> 00:34:23,204
Why are you telling me?
What does it have to do with me?

476
00:34:23,204 --> 00:34:24,624
It has nothing to do with you.

477
00:34:24,624 --> 00:34:26,184
So why were you looking at me?

478
00:34:26,184 --> 00:34:28,424
Can't I glance around? Can't I look at you?

479
00:34:28,424 --> 00:34:34,124
Kai, I'm doing my nails today.
Nobody's watching the shop.

480
00:34:34,124 --> 00:34:35,824
Ya En.

481
00:34:38,404 --> 00:34:41,824
I don't have time to pick up Jia Yu's, either.

482
00:34:44,704 --> 00:34:49,944
You're the best, Kai.
Ye Meng, let's get our nails done.

483
00:34:49,944 --> 00:34:51,964
Thank you for the bubble tea.

484
00:34:51,964 --> 00:34:54,304
You're both leaving?

485
00:34:54,304 --> 00:34:56,584
Tell you what, he's here for you.

486
00:34:56,584 --> 00:34:58,964
Don't try to freak me out in broad daylight.

487
00:34:58,964 --> 00:35:00,664
Seriously.

488
00:35:12,384 --> 00:35:14,184
Have this.

489
00:35:20,464 --> 00:35:26,844
Let's try that new open-air restaurant
at the night market? Okay.

490
00:35:26,844 --> 00:35:30,324
Dr. Gao, looking sharp. Got a date?

491
00:35:30,324 --> 00:35:34,104
Yeah, with the family member
of your former roommate.

492
00:35:36,504 --> 00:35:38,604
- Ye Meng? 
 - Yeah. That beautiful lady.

493
00:35:38,604 --> 00:35:40,204
No, it's not a date.

494
00:35:40,204 --> 00:35:43,724
I'm asking her for a favor.

495
00:35:43,724 --> 00:35:46,524
Mrs. Tou, let me check your leg.

496
00:35:47,544 --> 00:35:49,444
- Does it hurt? 
 - No.

497
00:35:49,444 --> 00:35:54,884
Mrs. Tou, your leg has healed.
You can basically go home now.

498
00:35:54,884 --> 00:35:57,284
But make sure to avoid strenuous activities.

499
00:35:57,284 --> 00:36:00,084
Okay, thank you.

500
00:36:00,084 --> 00:36:02,224
I'll make my rounds.

501
00:36:02,224 --> 00:36:04,264
Go ahead.

502
00:36:09,324 --> 00:36:16,004
What's going on with you and Ye Meng?
Why didn't you seize the opportunity?

503
00:36:16,004 --> 00:36:20,084
Forget it. The Ye family's different.
